<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="MTA95">
<l>nāvāyi luṇṭē namōnāra ṇāveṉ</l>
<l>ṟōvā turaikku muraiyuṇṭē – mūvāta</l>
<l>mākkatikkaṭ cellum vakaiyuṇṭē yeṉṉoruvar</l>
<l>tīkkatikkaṭ cellun tiṟam</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>There is a tongue in the mouth. There is speech that says</l>
<l>incessantly ‘obeisance, oh Nāraṇaṉ’. There is a means</l>
<l>to go the ageless great way. How can</l>
<l>someone go onto the path of evil?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
